// qterm1.cpp
// Fast Qt6 ANSI Terminal (single-file), extended VT100 support for full-screen apps.
// Added: mouse selection, copy & paste (clipboard), context menu.
// Target: Linux / macOS. Build with Qt6 Widgets (C++17).

